blog.title: phanfiction catalogue
blog.description:
mobile users, click here!

please refer to our FAQ first.

Our goal is to create an alphabetized library of every phanfiction in the phandom. Besides that, we compile masterlists of different genres that are scheduled for posting every few days, and help find fics that have been mislocated.

title: Praise!Kink (4) Masterlist
body:
part one, part two, part three

Aesthetics - flowers-and-colored-hair

Summary: Funded by Phil’s family money, Dam runs a pretentious aesthetic porn blog. One day, he gets an idea for a photoshoot, and he needs Phil’s help to do it, or more specifically, Phil’s mouth.

As You Please - botanistlester

Summary: In which Dan ruins the mood during sex. Except he doesn’t.

Caught (ao3) - hygge

Summary: Just because they weren’t together anymore didn’t mean that Dan couldn’t read phanfiction while he got off, right? Or at least that’s what he thought before Phil walked into the room.

Daddy’s Little Princess - phandomsub

Summary: Dan’s still a shy, easily-flustered virgin, but Phil can fix that. High school Pastel!Dan and Punk!Phil AU

Dance To This - melancholymango

Summary: After meeting on a questionable dating app, Dan and Phil make plans for a quick and easy hook-up. Dan wants to lose his virginity, and Phil is used to one night stands and short-term partners. What he isn’t used to is running into those partners again after they walk out on him.

Eggnog (With Rum) (ao3) - NonStopIsBack

Summary: A bit of really late Christmas smut to go with my last story.

Mon Cœur S'ouvre à Ta Voix - auroraphilealis

Summary: It’s taken Dan a year to work up the courage to really discover why he keeps slipping into something he doesn’t fully understand, but now that he’s discovered that he’s not alone, he’s ready to find a solution, even if that does mean accepting a Dom into his life. Thank God Phil is there to save him when things seem like they’re about to go wrong.

Phil Lester & The Downfall of Dateable London Men - gorgeousdan

Summary: Phil’s a YouTuber who’s certain he’ll never find love. Dan sends penis enlargement emails and wants to change Phil’s mind.

Phil Gets A Puppy - blissedoutphil

Summary: Phil wants a dog so much? Dan will give him one. Just, not how he expects it.

Sweet Boy - flowers-and-colored-hair

Summary: Dan is a wealthy omega who’s always bossing his not so wealthy beta friend, Phil, around. One day he goes too far and Phil puts the omega in his place.

The One Where Dan And Dan Trade Places - gorgeousdan

Summary: 30 year old Phil wakes up to a horny 18 year old Dan in his and Dan’s flat.

The Spell You Cast On Me (ao3) - crazed_peanut

Summary: Phil notices Dan is feeling stressed and they scene together.

The Vibrator Challenge (ao3) -  omgdatphantho

Summary: Dan and Phil participate in a challenge tag.

White Chocolate Kisses - somanydestiel

Summary: Sometimes Phil just needs to be praised and taken care of.

You glanced my way and gave me a wave (ao3) - NeverBeenAWriter

Summary: Phil walks in on something he shouldn’t and gets drawn in by the small looking boy in pastel pink.

You’re My Favorite Kind of Night - intphan

Summary: Dan rides Phil for the first time and basically it’s just PWP with a tid bit of fluff
